sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>SubscriptionPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>MySubscriptionView
    participant SER as UserSubscriptionSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to Subscription page
    FE->>API: GET /api/subscriptions/my-subscription/
    API->>DB: UserSubscription.objects.get(user=request.user)
    DB-->>API: UserSubscription instance
    API->>SER: UserSubscriptionSerializer(subscription)
    SER-->>API: Serialized subscription data
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {plan_name, features, expiry}
    FE-->>U: Display current plan details and tier comparison
